text: "Megatron" is a dancehall/hip-hop song by Nicki Minaj. It was released on June 21, 2019. It is her only solo released in 2019. The song has a sample of "Murder She Wrote" by Chaka Demus and Pliers. == References == Category:2019 songs Category:Nicki Minaj songs Category:Dancehall songs Category:Hip hop songs
title: Megatron (song)
